{"tid":1737524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［新重要戰術研究］古代盾陣","createTime":"2019-11-19T03:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T05:18:20.000Z","uid":274120,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c65e2cecdfccc0cae0782f635295cde2252d67fa","tid":1737524,"uid":274120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">首先希望大家唔好介意我係P牌仔</span><br />\n<br />\n其實都講咗好耐狗衝過尼唔好分開9散 好易拎前線落單俾人捉 盾陣係好緊要但我個人又覺得依家個傘陣/盾陣放狗衝過尼個成效比較弱 所以我覺得應該用返d古代戰爭智慧<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">（<span style=\"color: green;\">矛盾陣）</span></span> 如下圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hFZ78d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhFZ78d0.jpg&h=df29c65a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ecE78d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FecE78d0.jpg&h=b80e3c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然我哋好難整個矛出嚟 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">矛</span></span>可以用竹枝鐵支水管長棒取替（頭磨尖/加利器效果更佳）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">盾</span></span>就可以用返遮/任何做盾嘅物件<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">作用1：</span></span>防狗衝 狗重過嚟有一定阻嚇作用 盾可以令前線冇咁易被捕 矛又可以造成一定傷害擊退班狗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">作用2:</span></span>配合遠攻 盾矛陣可以令班狗衝過黎嗰陣唔係太靠近 呢個時候就可以用火魔水魔 磚 箭 反擊 距離拉近左容易擊中 同時又可以配合前線用矛吉佢地造成擊退效果 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">增強成攻率方法：</span><br />\n方法一： 講都講到厭 一定要破咗個心理關口 狗衝過尼好驚 堅守盾陣向前推進<br />\n方法二：長期使用直到到達前進目的地<br />\n方法三：要做就一定要成排都係盾 咁就唔會咁容易搵到突破口<br />\n方法四：最前排每一個人要一手揸矛一手揸盾（唔夠人嘅情況）<br />\n一個人揸矛一個人揸盾（夠人嘅情況）<br />\n<br />\n同意就推俾比前線睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例子可以睇返啲復古戰爭片 e.g.魔戒  <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後千祈千祈唔好吉親啲曱甴</span></span>"},{"pid":"d91b35cc440772125f7f31ed4d795d311d9a411f","tid":1737524,"uid":70771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:43:50.000Z","msg":"咪姐係遮陣進化版, 難免又會變陣地戰, 唔好FF真係可以軍隊式咁樣向前進, 同埋對家已經係用實彈+冇後果要顧, 我唔同意所以拉"},{"pid":"97b23b5fd9496b3d25d3cfa052b112cca362f316","tid":1737524,"uid":107726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"冷氣夠未？"},{"pid":"84f9bde72292931b59a172ef3d67b2f470d7f6c8","tid":1737524,"uid":219583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:48:01.000Z","msg":"咪撚打機上腦啦白痴<br />\n你戰狼300有無tg射埋去呀柒頭<br />\n水炮車一射就散啦 無撚腦真係你呢d廢閪"},{"pid":"f377ee95f38edd870f08cca3412cfd36f710386c","tid":1737524,"uid":17732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"師兄你原意係好<br />\n但琴日一戰重未明？<br />\n個武力差太遠.....郁下都實彈 你點打..."},{"pid":"85cd4259351041cfe2cf57c9fed0b49c77175a04","tid":1737524,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"5.56<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f785854e9e4e58f1fb54fe86976f6ba35f797d3a","tid":1737524,"uid":274120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:50:28.000Z","msg":"符片哈比人五軍之戰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m0fGtrf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm0fGtrf.gif&h=0f5d85c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63ac12d96987d81d91f03ca49185740d9c48f558","tid":1737524,"uid":70088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"一架裝甲車埋黎<br />\n<br />\n你會點？"},{"pid":"1e4b045035e841de4868fc27e17cf9635f6ffc8b","tid":1737524,"uid":274120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d91b35cc440772125f7f31ed4d795d311d9a411f","tid":1737524,"uid":70771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:43:50.000Z","msg":"咪姐係遮